<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer12471987863226585089">Ingalls wrote a series of historical fiction books for children based on her childhood growing up in a pioneer family. She also wrote a regular newspaper column and kept a diary as an adult moving from South Dakota to Missouri, the latter of which has been published as a book.</span>

